WEBVTT

1
00:02:09.086 --> 00:02:12.716
Oh. I-I… I think…
I think you're in the erroneous apartment.

2
00:02:27.606 --> 00:02:29.024
What the… What…

3
00:02:38.825 --> 00:02:40.244
Fuck.

4
00:03:05.936 --> 00:03:07.604
I like the viscosity.

5
00:03:09.231 --> 00:03:11.316
- Let's see how it freezes.
- On it.

6
00:03:41.805 --> 00:03:43.681
Hi.

7
00:03:43.682 --> 00:03:45.183
Sorry I'm late.

8
00:03:45.184 --> 00:03:48.311
Hey.
How's my favorite food scientist?

9
00:03:48.312 --> 00:03:49.604
Good.

10
00:03:49.605 --> 00:03:51.772
- Just busy. busy.
- <i>All right.</i>

11
00:03:51.773 --> 00:03:53.817
<i>Shall we start experimenting?</i>

12
00:03:56.820 --> 00:03:57.946
Yeah.

13
00:03:59.323 --> 00:04:01.532
<i>Good. Uh-huh.</i>

14
00:04:01.533 --> 00:04:02.909
Okay. stop.

15
00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:04.493
Tell me what you know.

16
00:04:04.494 --> 00:04:06.120
This is humiliating.

17
00:04:06.121 --> 00:04:07.539
I was going through a break-up.

18
00:04:08.123 --> 00:04:09.457
Trevor DMed me on Instagram.

19
00:04:09.458 --> 00:04:12.752
He was charming. I was lonely. we flirted.

20
00:04:12.753 --> 00:04:14.254
- Mmm.
- He made me feel good.

21
00:04:15.047 --> 00:04:17.631
And then he asked me
if I wanted to video chat and…

22
00:04:17.632 --> 00:04:19.717
So dumb.

23
00:04:19.718 --> 00:04:23.638
No. trust me. I feel the same way
and we're not the only victims either.

24
00:04:23.639 --> 00:04:25.389
I'm just trying
to figure out what happened.

25
00:04:25.390 --> 00:04:27.934
Obviously. I had no idea
he was recording me.

26
00:04:27.935 --> 00:04:30.311
Then one day a guy shows up
and he had that video.

27
00:04:30.312 --> 00:04:32.898
- Okay. was this the guy?
- Yeah. that's him.

28
00:04:33.774 --> 00:04:37.402
He said he'd leak the video to everyone
if I didn't comply.

29
00:04:38.487 --> 00:04:39.862
How much money did he want?

30
00:04:39.863 --> 00:04:42.573
Nothing. Oh. I offered him money.
but he didn't want it.

31
00:04:42.574 --> 00:04:44.158
He said I'd have to do…

32
00:04:44.159 --> 00:04:45.243
…exactly what he said.

33
00:04:45.244 --> 00:04:47.787
- Exactly as he said it.
- Mmm.

34
00:04:47.788 --> 00:04:50.957
Or he would ruin my life.
He knew everything.

35
00:04:50.958 --> 00:04:53.876
- My family. my friends. I begged him…
- Sorry.

36
00:04:53.877 --> 00:04:56.255
…but there was just no way
I could get out.

37
00:05:00.551 --> 00:05:02.093
Um… So. sorry.

38
00:05:02.094 --> 00:05:06.722
if the blackmailer didn't want money.
then what did he want?

39
00:05:06.723 --> 00:05:10.768
He wanted the specs
for a new strain of fast-rising yeast

40
00:05:10.769 --> 00:05:12.187
that we were about to patent.

41
00:05:12.855 --> 00:05:15.273
- Yeast?
- It took years to develop.

42
00:05:15.274 --> 00:05:18.568
The patent is easily worth
tens of millions in revenue.

43
00:05:18.569 --> 00:05:21.153
You saw that video.
That's clearly my office.

44
00:05:21.154 --> 00:05:22.572
My life would have been destroyed.

45
00:05:22.573 --> 00:05:24.908
So I gave him what he wanted.

46
00:05:25.742 --> 00:05:27.618
So that was it? There's nothing else?

47
00:05:27.619 --> 00:05:30.621
A few months later. Northeastern
Food Group beat us to the patent.

48
00:05:30.622 --> 00:05:34.584
Stock value plummeted.
our whole company's downsizing.

49
00:05:34.585 --> 00:05:36.378
and I'm out of here
at the end of the month.

50
00:05:36.962 --> 00:05:38.880
Do you think Northeastern
was behind all of this?

51
00:05:38.881 --> 00:05:41.632
I have no idea. All I know is I'm fucked.

52
00:05:41.633 --> 00:05:45.679
If I can't figure this out soon… me too.

53
00:05:55.731 --> 00:05:57.857
<i>I kinda. like. never did this before.</i>

54
00:05:59.276 --> 00:06:01.402
<i>I guess I am kind of cute.</i>

55
00:06:01.403 --> 00:06:03.905
<i>That's right.
Eat that banana. you chubby monkey.</i>

56
00:06:03.906 --> 00:06:05.615
<i>Damn. Trevor. you look great.</i>

57
00:06:16.710 --> 00:06:18.045
Fucker.

58
00:06:18.545 --> 00:06:20.796
Uh… Angela?

59
00:06:20.797 --> 00:06:22.006
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

60
00:06:23.091 --> 00:06:24.634
Hi. I'm… I'm Paula.

61
00:06:24.635 --> 00:06:26.010
How did you get my name?

62
00:06:26.011 --> 00:06:27.553
- Uh. I'm Paula.
<i>- How did you find me?</i>

63
00:06:27.554 --> 00:06:29.430
- Are you a part of this?
- No. I really am not.

64
00:06:29.431 --> 00:06:30.848
…wanted some information exclusive to

65
00:06:30.849 --> 00:06:33.851
<i>a client and our company.
I wanted it to end.</i>

66
00:06:33.852 --> 00:06:36.229
He didn't want money.
He wanted my influence on some votes.

67
00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:38.315
He wanted a bunch of zoning permits.

68
00:06:41.276 --> 00:06:42.277
Fuck.

69
00:06:48.367 --> 00:06:49.576
Crap.

70
00:06:57.918 --> 00:06:59.169
What are you looking for?

71
00:06:59.753 --> 00:07:02.506
A 5'8" prison guard with coffee breath.

72
00:07:03.423 --> 00:07:05.175
Oh. look. Thank you. God.

73
00:07:08.011 --> 00:07:09.638
Thursday 8:15.

74
00:07:13.892 --> 00:07:15.269
Son of a bitch.

75
00:07:15.811 --> 00:07:17.688
Thursday 9:17. Look.

76
00:07:18.814 --> 00:07:20.274
Two Rebecca Hallidays.

77
00:07:20.774 --> 00:07:21.817
Two different signatures.

78
00:07:24.069 --> 00:07:25.195
Oh. yeah.

79
00:07:26.780 --> 00:07:28.865
I'm gonna need the security footage
from both these visitors.

80
00:07:28.866 --> 00:07:31.200
And the feed from the parking lot.

81
00:07:31.201 --> 00:07:33.953
- I'm gonna need their cars and plates.
- I got it.

82
00:07:33.954 --> 00:07:37.373
Hey. Two lawyers with the same name
came to visit Paula.

83
00:07:37.374 --> 00:07:39.625
- She was telling the truth.
<i>- Oh. shit.</i>

84
00:07:39.626 --> 00:07:42.670
And Dennis O'Neill is not answering
his phone. Straight to voicemail.

85
00:07:42.671 --> 00:07:44.046
I'm on the lawyer.

86
00:07:44.047 --> 00:07:47.425
- You go to Dennis's house. Find him.
- <i>All right. I'm on it. But hey. G.</i>

87
00:07:47.426 --> 00:07:50.344
every once in a while. you gotta throw
a motherfucking please in there.

88
00:07:50.345 --> 00:07:51.471
Motherfucking please.

89
00:07:52.389 --> 00:07:53.765
Better.

90
00:07:59.438 --> 00:08:01.106
There's my Jennifer.

91
00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:03.358
- What's what?
- <i>Everything should be buttoned up.</i>

92
00:08:03.942 --> 00:08:06.027
I met with Paula Sanders.
She doesn't know anything.

93
00:08:06.028 --> 00:08:09.280
But she did have Dennis's burner phone
which I retrieved.

94
00:08:09.281 --> 00:08:12.200
The only minor wrinkle
is there was a single contact on it.

95
00:08:12.201 --> 00:08:14.535
Mmm. That sounds pretty wrinkly.

96
00:08:14.536 --> 00:08:16.245
Like a linen suit in a duffel bag.

97
00:08:16.246 --> 00:08:18.831
Nah. man. he was a pro.
There can't be much exposure.

98
00:08:18.832 --> 00:08:22.084
Look. I'm out of town the rest of
this week on a company retreat.

99
00:08:22.085 --> 00:08:25.087
Before I return. find this Paula person.

100
00:08:25.088 --> 00:08:26.923
