101
00:08:26.924 --> 00:08:28.049
- You understand me?
- <i>Yep.</i>

102
00:08:28.050 --> 00:08:30.218
- Sounds like a plan. my man.
- <i>Wonderful.</i>

103
00:08:30.219 --> 00:08:33.304
And. hey. don't ever call me
while you're fucking eating.

104
00:08:47.236 --> 00:08:48.237
I love it.

105
00:08:53.242 --> 00:08:54.243
Hey.

106
00:08:57.204 --> 00:08:58.205
Pauls.

107
00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:02.250
- You're. uh… You're here.
- Yeah. I mean…

108
00:09:02.251 --> 00:09:04.544
The whole way over.
I was wondering.

109
00:09:04.545 --> 00:09:07.422
"Is this crazy. my being here?" But…

110
00:09:08.549 --> 00:09:10.299
Today's about Hazel. it's not about me.

111
00:09:10.300 --> 00:09:13.177
It's not in your head. Everybody knows
what happened. They all know.

112
00:09:13.178 --> 00:09:14.470
You can't be here.

113
00:09:14.471 --> 00:09:16.514
- I-I… I mean…
- Paula. you realize that. right?

114
00:09:16.515 --> 00:09:18.683
I… I promised her. so I'm not gonna go.

115
00:09:18.684 --> 00:09:20.476
- I understand. but. Paula. you can't...
- And I'm innocent.

116
00:09:20.477 --> 00:09:21.853
I didn't fucking do anything.

117
00:09:21.854 --> 00:09:23.272
Okay. I believe you.

118
00:09:23.981 --> 00:09:28.192
I also believe
that you shouldn't be here. okay?

119
00:09:28.193 --> 00:09:30.486
- It's not going to end well.
- Yeah.

120
00:09:30.487 --> 00:09:31.697
You see that. right?

121
00:09:32.281 --> 00:09:33.698
- I mean. you must.
- Yeah. Oh!

122
00:09:33.699 --> 00:09:35.157
- I don't see how this...
- Reinforcements.

123
00:09:35.158 --> 00:09:37.368
Hey. Paula. How's it… Um…

124
00:09:37.369 --> 00:09:39.829
Wh-What are you doing here?

125
00:09:39.830 --> 00:09:42.291
Hey. Mal. You probably want me
to go in there. right?

126
00:09:43.417 --> 00:09:46.794
Right? 'Cause then I could cause a scene
and then you could win custody.

127
00:09:46.795 --> 00:09:49.673
I wasn't thinking about custody.
I was thinking about Hazel.

128
00:09:50.299 --> 00:09:52.592
Everyone knows. She doesn't.

129
00:09:52.593 --> 00:09:55.428
If you go in there.
she will figure it out.

130
00:09:55.429 --> 00:09:56.763
It's unavoidable.

131
00:09:58.682 --> 00:10:00.225
What do you want to happen?

132
00:10:00.809 --> 00:10:03.770
Do you want her to figure this out
like this. Paula?

133
00:10:04.855 --> 00:10:09.860
Please. Think about this.
Think about what you're doing right now.

134
00:10:26.585 --> 00:10:29.420
No. no-no one broke my laptop.

135
00:10:29.421 --> 00:10:31.089
It literally just stopped working.
It was so weird.

136
00:10:31.673 --> 00:10:33.841
Okay. well. what's the point
of having insurance if I...

137
00:10:33.842 --> 00:10:35.636
What the hell?

138
00:10:38.805 --> 00:10:41.516
- Why do you look like shit?
- I was attacked with my own bong.

139
00:10:41.517 --> 00:10:43.769
A bong?
Are you in middle school?

140
00:10:44.353 --> 00:10:46.854
I think you're missing the headline
while trying to mock me.

141
00:10:46.855 --> 00:10:49.106
- I was attacked.
- What happened?

142
00:10:49.107 --> 00:10:51.901
Some woman broke into my apartment.
brutalized me

143
00:10:51.902 --> 00:10:53.611
and then stole back that burner phone.

144
00:10:53.612 --> 00:10:55.072
The burner phone that you stole from me?

145
00:10:55.656 --> 00:10:57.156
Oh. my God. Yes.

146
00:10:57.157 --> 00:10:59.242
Okay. it's just
an endless cycle of criminality.

147
00:10:59.243 --> 00:11:01.994
God. you really focus
on. like. the pettiest shit.

148
00:11:01.995 --> 00:11:03.704
All right. why would someone attack me
for that phone?

149
00:11:03.705 --> 00:11:05.039
Paula must have been telling the truth.

150
00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:07.250
Except there was nothing on it.

151
00:11:07.251 --> 00:11:09.670
Well. it must have some value. Geri.
'cause…

152
00:11:10.379 --> 00:11:11.463
look at my head.

153
00:11:12.047 --> 00:11:14.173
We need to go tell Paula. Come on.

154
00:11:14.174 --> 00:11:15.175
Mmm.

155
00:11:16.468 --> 00:11:18.135
Sixty-eight percent of me is with you.

156
00:11:18.136 --> 00:11:21.430
But the other 32% is like. "Fuck you"
for breaking my laptop.

157
00:11:21.431 --> 00:11:23.850
Well. you lied to me first.
Right?

158
00:11:23.851 --> 00:11:25.394
And that actually hurt.

159
00:11:27.604 --> 00:11:28.605
