extenuating circumstances.

234
00:15:43.694 --> 00:15:45.069
courts are busy. blah-blah-blah.

235
00:15:45.070 --> 00:15:47.655
Oh. my God.
How am I supposed to get a fair hearing

236
00:15:47.656 --> 00:15:50.116
when I've just been arrested
for fucking murder?

237
00:15:50.117 --> 00:15:52.243
<i>Well. you're innocent
and you're a great mom</i>

238
00:15:52.244 --> 00:15:54.745
and we will make
both points clear in court.

239
00:15:54.746 --> 00:15:55.747
<i>There's another thing.</i>

240
00:15:56.456 --> 00:15:59.375
- Don't panic.
- I'm panicking. What? What?

241
00:15:59.376 --> 00:16:02.003
Karl and Mallory are petitioning
for full custody.

242
00:16:02.004 --> 00:16:04.005
Now this isn't just about Idaho anymore.

243
00:16:04.006 --> 00:16:06.757
If they win.
they'll control your access to Hazel.

244
00:16:06.758 --> 00:16:08.718
They can't fucking do that!

245
00:16:08.719 --> 00:16:10.887
<i>They can try.
and we will try and stop them.</i>

246
00:16:10.888 --> 00:16:13.140
<i>We will get through this.
All right? Talk to you soon.</i>

247
00:16:13.724 --> 00:16:15.099
What a shit show.

248
00:16:18.896 --> 00:16:19.979
